pear2.php.net/P1 depends on: pear2.php.net/P2 (>= 1.1.0,<= 2.0.0,!= [1.2.0,1.2.3],recommends 1.3.1)
', $e->getPrevious()->getMessage(), 'cause message');
}
\pear2\Pyrus\Installer::rollback();
